 <p style="text-indent: 0.5in;"><span style="font-size: 14pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 'KG Miss Kindergarten';">Edge Academy is helping readers to grow and experience the love of reading through new books! Many teachers have found generous sponsors so every child in their rooms has a new book to keep every month. This makes such a difference in so many children’s lives and education. They have the joy of receiving a book every month that they can take home, read, and reread. New books are always fun and they help build the students love of reading. Every student looks forward to it and the teachers are filled with excitement and joy as they watch their students receive this treasure from September to May. Last year there were a few classes and this year several more teachers are participating.</span></p>
